name: RYUON-manual
tagline: overview and tutorials of RYUON for users
body:
### Welcome to RYUON-manual Pages.
"RYUON-manual" contains TeX sources describing overview and tutorials of the [RYUON project](http://kichiki.github.com/ryuon/) for users.

### about RYUON project
"RYUON-manual" is a part of [RYUON project](http://kichiki.github.com/ryuon/).

The result can be seen at "[RYUON - a Particle Simulation Suite](http://kichiki.github.com/ryuon/docs/manual/)"

### Authors and Contributors
Kengo Ichiki (@kichiki)
